Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.20,0:01:50.54,Default,,0,0,0,,THE DECIDING MOMENT
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.71,0:01:52.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Take this!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.84,0:01:54.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}Raiden!{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.10,0:02:08.39,Default,,0,0,0,,It worked!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.81,0:02:13.02,Default,,0,0,0,,We did it! Hooray! Hooray!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.23,0:02:19.28,Default,,0,0,0,,As expected, his armour's fine,\Nbut I bet he's burned to a crisp in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.82,0:02:24.49,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what you get\Nfor underestimating us, right Dai?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.21,0:02:33.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Popp!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.96,0:02:38.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Even Raiden didn't work?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.97,0:02:41.22,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it worked.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.84,0:02:45.81,Default,,0,0,0,,But he withstood the damage from it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.22,0:02:49.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Even without his armour,\NHyunckel's strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.19,0:02:52.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I misjudged you two.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.31,0:02:56.65,Default,,0,0,0,,If you can do this,\Nthen there's no need to hold back.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.36,0:02:59.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Here goes!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.65,0:03:02.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai, one more!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.61,0:03:05.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Too late!\N{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}Tomakugutsosho!{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.28,0:03:06.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}Rai...{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.83,0:03:08.50,Default,,0,0,0,,That binding thing again!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.66,0:03:11.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Farewell!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.33,0:03:15.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}Bloody Sukuraido!{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.51,0:03:22.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We can't beat him.\NNot by sword or by magic.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.14,0:03:26.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.43,0:03:30.68,Default,,0,0,0,,It's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.40,0:03:37.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it must be an exit!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.15,0:03:41.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Hang in there, Dai!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.40,0:03:42.61,Default,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.78,0:03:45.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Answer me, Dai! Dai!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.78,0:03:49.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't bother.\NBloody Sukuraido! is a killing attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.87,0:03:51.08,Default,,0,0,0,,He's finished.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.25,0:03:52.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.00,0:03:58.71,Default,,0,0,0,,This is all my fault! I got Dai killed!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.88,0:04:01.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Join him in the afterlife.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.13,0:04:03.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, Hyunckel!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.18,0:04:08.85,Default,,0,0,0,,When did you get out?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.18,0:04:10.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Hyunckel, how could you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.52,0:04:15.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You've struck a fellow Disciple of Avan!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.44,0:04:19.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't give me that.\NHe's a student of my father's killer!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.03,0:04:24.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You're wrong!\NMaster Avan wasn't your father's killer!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.36,0:04:25.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Spare me the lies!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.70,0:04:27.24,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the truth!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.16,0:04:30.62,Default,,0,0,0,,This was in a chest in a hidden room.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.00,0:04:32.83,Default,,0,0,0,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.46,0:04:34.87,Default,,0,0,0,,a Soul Shell!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.50,0:04:38.63,Default,,0,0,0,,They contain messages from the dying!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.29,0:04:44.34,Default,,0,0,0,,It's from your father.\NThe last words of the Hell Knight Bartos!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.72,0:04:47.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad's last words?! Impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.80,0:04:49.93,Default,,0,0,0,,How could that exist?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.35,0:04:52.93,Default,,0,0,0,,This isn't happening.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.39,0:04:56.77,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way he's dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.98,0:05:01.15,Default,,0,0,0,,He's alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.90,0:05:11.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}In that instant, he leaned his body back\Nand avoided a hit to his heart!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.46,0:05:16.79,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't... beat him...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.33,0:05:22.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He can't be beaten by sword.\NHe can't be beaten by magic.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.80,0:05:24.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Not by sword or by magic.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.76,0:05:26.13,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't beat him!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.47,0:05:31.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.22,0:05:36.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen, Hyunckel,\Nto the truth your father left behind!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.31,0:05:42.94,Default,,0,0,0,,What really happened\Nthe day this Underground Palace fell!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.94,0:05:46.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hyunckel... My son...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.07,0:05:47.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.53,0:05:54.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My dear son, Hyunckel.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.66,0:06:00.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I leave this message\Nso that you will know the truth.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.83,0:06:04.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The day the hero's party\Nattacked the Underground Palace,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.42,0:06:08.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I fought Avan, the Hero\Nas keeper of the Hell Gate!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.47,0:06:11.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But Avan was strong.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.02,0:06:22.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I prepared for my death.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.48,0:06:23.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And then...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.90,0:06:29.15,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?! Strike me down!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.82,0:06:30.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's not do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.99,0:06:34.08,Default,,0,0,0,,What?! Will you shame me with your mercy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.00,0:06:40.33,Default,,0,0,0,,That was clearly made by a child's hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.50,0:06:44.84,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems unlikely, but you have a family.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.09,0:06:50.18,Default,,0,0,0,,When I realized that, I couldn't kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.30,0:06:57.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You've beaten me. Not just in strength,\Nbut in heart as well!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.06,0:07:00.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Now please open the gate.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.69,0:07:03.90,Default,,0,0,0,,The only one I'm here for is Hadlar.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.15,0:07:08.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir Hero! I have something I must ask you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.49,0:07:12.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And so I told him.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.41,0:07:15.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}How I found and raised a human child.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.29,0:07:21.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And that, even if he spared me,\Nshould Hadlar die, I would cease to be.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.58,0:07:26.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Hero Avan! Please look after my son!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.55,0:07:29.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Raise him to be a strong,\Nrighteous warrior!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.92,0:07:34.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I ask that you show him real human warmth!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.26,0:07:36.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.81,0:07:41.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sir Avan gracefully accepted.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.19,0:07:46.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And then Sir Avan went to face Hadlar.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.03,0:07:52.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Soon after...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.57,0:07:58.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hadlar's death cry\Nechoed through the palace!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.70,0:08:04.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And yet... I still lived.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.30,0:08:13.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Lord Hadlar!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.93,0:08:15.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You survived?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.84,0:08:17.43,Default,,0,0,0,,At my moment of death,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.60,0:08:21.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I was saved by the dark powers\Nof the Underworld god, Vearn!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.81,0:08:24.23,Default,,0,0,0,,The Underworld god, Vearn?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.40,0:08:30.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I must now sleep for 13 years to build up\Nmy power and create a new Dark Army!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.11,0:08:35.57,Default,,0,0,0,,An army far greater\Nthan the current Dark Army!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.95,0:08:40.29,Default,,0,0,0,,But, before I do that,\NI need to execute you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.79,0:08:42.16,Default,,0,0,0,,M-Me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.66,0:08:45.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You're an absolute failure!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.29,0:08:48.79,Default,,0,0,0,,With your pathetic sense of justice\Nand chivalry!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.96,0:08:51.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Your human-like warmth makes you weak!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.51,0:08:57.72,Default,,0,0,0,,And on top of that, you let Avan\Npass right through the Hell Gate!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.18,0:09:00.18,Default,,0,0,0,,When I create my new Dark Army,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.35,0:09:04.81,Default,,0,0,0,,it will have no place\Nfor a mistake like you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.61,0:09:12.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, Avan, enjoy your moment of peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.94,0:09:17.36,Default,,0,0,0,,When my new Dark Army is complete,\NI'll come for you first!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.95,0:09:22.41,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Hyunckel...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.50,0:09:27.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.50,0:09:30.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.22,0:09:36.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Hyunckel...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.97,0:09:41.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I no longer had the strength\Nto tell you the truth.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.35,0:09:46.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And so I hid this message in secret\Nwithin this Soul Shell.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.14,0:09:51.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hoping that one day, you would hear it.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.53,0:09:57.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hyunckel, I hope that\Nyou live like a human.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.57,0:10:00.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And you must not hate Sir Avan!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.70,0:10:06.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If anything, hate this foolish monster\Nwho deemed to raise a human child.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.50,0:10:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But know that I was happy.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.17,0:10:16.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}For a brief moment,\Nthis cold corpse of a body felt warmth.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.42,0:10:20.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Please let me say this one more time...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.55,0:10:26.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hyunckel... thank you for the memories...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.77,0:10:28.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Dad!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.69,0:10:34.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Then Hadlar was the one\Nwho killed my father?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.61,0:10:41.37,Default,,0,0,0,,And Avan knew I thought\Nhe killed my father...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.74,0:10:44.62,Default,,0,0,0,,and still looked after me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.37,0:10:47.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Lies...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.33,0:10:50.04,Default,,0,0,0,,All lies!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.63,0:10:55.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Sword... and magic...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.59,0:10:59.09,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Hey Dai?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.97,0:11:02.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Sword... and magic...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.64,0:11:04.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait! Dai!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.14,0:11:08.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Something's wrong.\NIt's like he doesn't know who I am.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.06,0:11:12.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Are you telling me\Nhe's not even conscious?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.27,0:11:13.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.11,0:11:18.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Impossible! A direct hit\Nwith Bloody Sukuraido! and he still lives?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.99,0:11:27.49,On Top,,0,0,0,,MAGIC BULLET GUN
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.00,0:11:32.50,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}BLOODY SUKURAIDO!{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.29,0:11:38.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I remember Master Avan mentioning this.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.42,0:11:44.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sometimes martial artists can keep on\Nfighting even after being knocked out.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.68,0:11:48.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Like their battle instincts keep on going.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.18,0:11:51.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That must be what's happening with Dai!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.85,0:11:55.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai, don't! He'll kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.23,0:11:59.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Curse you.\NI'll finish you for sure this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.61,0:12:03.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop! You heard what your father said!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.41,0:12:07.33,Default,,0,0,0,,The Dark Lord Hadlar is the one\Nyou should really hate!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.49,0:12:09.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop using your sword for evil!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.45,0:12:10.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.67,0:12:15.04,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no turning back for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.42,0:12:18.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm the Undead Legion Commander\Nof the Dark Army!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.46,0:12:24.59,Default,,0,0,0,,With my body encased in this dark armour,\NI am the vengeful warrior, Hyunckel!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.76,0:12:27.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Hyunckel...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.94,0:12:37.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Here goes, Dai!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.66,0:12:47.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Magic and sword...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.49,0:12:50.04,Default,,0,0,0,,It's no good!\NHe doesn't have his usual speed!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.20,0:12:51.16,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the end!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.33,0:12:53.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Magic... and sword!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.54,0:12:58.75,Default,,0,0,0,,What?! My supreme armour!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.88,0:13:02.09,Default,,0,0,0,,His sword burns?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.84,0:13:04.97,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the flame of a Mera spell!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.13,0:13:07.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No one can encase a weapon in magic!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.55,0:13:14.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If anyone could, they would have to be\Nsomething beyond human!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.49,0:13:28.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes! Dai was able to create\Na new attack in this moment of peril!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.16,0:13:32.87,Default,,0,0,0,,When neither magic\Nnor sword worked alone, he used both...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.04,0:13:34.33,Default,,0,0,0,,in a Magic Sword!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.50,0:13:35.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Curse you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.85,0:13:52.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice! Do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.73,0:14:01.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.65,0:14:06.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't miss this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.49,0:14:08.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I've gotta do something!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.53,0:14:11.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The thunderclouds I summoned...!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.16,0:14:16.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai, the lightning!\NCall down the lighting!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.87,0:14:19.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Lightning...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.46,0:14:22.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Give it up! I'll finish it with this!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.13,0:14:26.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Lightning... Call lightning...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.59,0:14:28.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Call down the lightning!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.43,0:14:32.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Take this! {\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}Bloody Sukuraido!{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.02,0:14:36.81,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.98,0:14:39.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\\i1}{\\3c&H1717E4&}Raiden...{\\i0}{\\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.40,0:14:43.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\\i1}{\\3c&H1717E4&}Strash!{\\i0}{\\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.37,0:14:57.00,Default,,0,0,0,,He did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.16,0:15:01.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Incomplete or not, it's an Avan Strash\Nand Raiden double whammy!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.63,0:15:04.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Not even Hyunckel can withstand...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.43,0:15:12.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is he immortal?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.52,0:15:25.77,Default,,0,0,0,,We won! We won!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.61,0:15:34.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's no good. I'm finished!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.08,0:15:37.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai, that's enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.45,0:15:39.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Maam?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.04,0:15:44.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai, it's all over! You've won!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.92,0:15:50.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Please... I don't want to see\Nthe Disciples of Avan fighting each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.18,0:15:54.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Tears?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.57,0:16:09.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Maam? Hyunckel?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.86,0:16:11.28,Default,,0,0,0,,What was I doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.45,0:16:12.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.07,0:16:14.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.87,0:16:16.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm your enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.83,0:16:18.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not our enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.25,0:16:23.71,Default,,0,0,0,,That's my...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.30,0:16:32.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You kept it this whole time?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.22,0:16:37.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew that the time would come\Nwhen I would return this to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.31,0:16:43.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This kindness... This caring warmth...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.73,0:16:46.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She's like...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.56,0:16:49.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}a holy mother.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.74,0:16:57.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai, are you okay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.62,0:17:02.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Popp, Gomechan... Did I win?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.20,0:17:03.33,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.50,0:17:04.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.04,0:17:06.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.50,0:17:07.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Hyunckel.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.09,0:17:18.51,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing, Maam?!\NWhat if he comes at us again?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.68,0:17:20.89,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no need to worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.06,0:17:23.93,Default,,0,0,0,,And shouldn't I get healed first?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.19,0:17:32.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm still casting Behoimi!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.74,0:17:33.82,Default,,0,0,0,,It's enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.99,0:17:39.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Just look at you, Hyunckel!\NLosing and then getting a lap pillow!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.74,0:17:42.16,Default,,0,0,0,,It's so pathetic it's hilarious!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.33,0:17:45.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You're.. Flazzard!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.29,0:17:49.38,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right! The mightiest\Nof the Six Legion Commanders!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.54,0:17:52.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Blizzblaze General Flazzard!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.67,0:17:56.30,Default,,0,0,0,,What is that guy?!\NHe's fire and ice stuck together!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.47,0:17:58.22,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.39,0:18:04.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't it obvious?!\NI thought I'd drop by and kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.85,0:18:09.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You know I've never liked you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.94,0:18:15.28,Default,,0,0,0,,A human trying to take all the credit?!\NNever in a million years!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.82,0:18:20.24,Default,,0,0,0,,If you'd won, I figured I'd kill you\Nand take the credit.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.41,0:18:23.45,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's even better that you lost!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.62,0:18:29.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll say you all killed each other\Nand spare you the shame!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.33,0:18:32.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You can cry and thank me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.38,0:18:36.13,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.80,0:18:41.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I just gave this extinct volcano\Na little wake-up call!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.35,0:18:44.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Soon this place'll be\Noverflowing with magma!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.93,0:18:45.93,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.02,0:18:53.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Curse you, Flazzard!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.86,0:18:57.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoops! Looks like I ain't welcome!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.61,0:18:59.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Guess I'll be bowing out now!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.11,0:19:00.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Everybody!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.66,0:19:05.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Enjoy your swim in the lava!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.08,0:19:09.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It's no good! We can't escape!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.37,0:19:11.71,Default,,0,0,0,,If we can make it up there...!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.88,0:19:14.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Nobody has that kind of strength left!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.56,0:19:31.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Hyunckel?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.77,0:19:35.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't let any of you die here!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.94,0:19:41.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Crocodine, I finally understand\Nhow you felt!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.99,0:19:45.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I hope I can apologize to you\Nin the afterlife.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.58,0:19:48.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But for now, for just an instant...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.95,0:19:53.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}lend me your titan strength!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.75,0:19:58.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop! Don't do it, Hyunckel!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.77,0:20:08.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Hyunckel!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.35,0:20:11.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Hyunckel!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.85,0:20:15.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Thank you.\NAt long last, my eyes are finally open.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.44,0:20:20.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I wish I could help you three out more...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.28,0:20:24.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}but it looks like this is as far as I go.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.66,0:20:26.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Hyunckel!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.03,0:20:29.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Watch out! This place won't last!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.41,0:20:30.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Maam!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.20,0:20:32.21,Default,,0,0,0,,It's coming down! We've got to go!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.37,0:20:34.67,Default,,0,0,0,,But Hyunckel's still...!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.17,0:20:38.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Farewell, Dai and Popp...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.71,0:20:42.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Goodbye... Maam...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.01,0:20:45.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Hyunckel!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.14,0:20:56.73,Default,,0,0,0,,And so the Undead Legion ends.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.90,0:21:02.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Master Hyunckel, at least let this\Nhumble Moruge guide you to the afterlife.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.24,0:21:10.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I hear the Underground Palace\Nwas destroyed.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.54,0:21:14.29,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems that extinct volcano\Nsuddenly erupted.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.46,0:21:16.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}An extinct volcano erupting?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.04,0:21:20.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh. That a shame.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.76,0:21:23.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, so be it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.01,0:21:29.30,Default,,0,0,0,,He took the new Hero out with him,\Nso I'd say that wasn't a bad job.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.85,0:21:31.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The audacity...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.56,0:21:40.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}How terrifying it is\Nto see a man starved for glory.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.57,0:21:45.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay! Now that Hyunckel's dead,\NI guess conquering the Holkia continent
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.57,0:21:47.41,Default,,0,0,0,,is my job now!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.95,0:21:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, all I gotta do is find\Nlittle Princess Leona and kill her!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.16,0:21:58.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Talk about an easy job!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.15,0:22:25.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kindness is the magic of kind people{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.15,0:22:25.90,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}yasashisa wa yasashii hito ga tsukaeru mahou{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.07,0:22:32.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Then do I have no choice\NBut to just be a normal person?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.07,0:22:32.91,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}jaa boku wa tada no hito de iru shikanaino?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.08,0:22:36.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm not sure{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.08,0:22:36.12,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}doudarou{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.42,0:22:44.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even if the place I call home may change{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.42,0:22:44.09,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}kaeru basho wa ne kawatte yuku kedo{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.25,0:22:46.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Listen to me, Mother{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.25,0:22:46.63,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}naa kaasan boku wa{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.80,0:22:52.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I will never change those I protect{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.80,0:22:52.76,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}mamoru hito wo kaetari shinai{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.22,0:22:57.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I wonder what you'd say{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.22,0:22:57.43,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}anata wa nannte iukana{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.60,0:23:01.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}At times I can be cowardly and small{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.60,0:23:01.65,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}tokiyori yowaki de chippoke de{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.81,0:23:08.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What would you say to me\NAs I hesitate to even hesitate?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.81,0:23:08.11,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}mayou koto ni mo mayou boku ni nannte iukana{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.28,0:23:13.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Unlike the today that I sought{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.28,0:23:13.95,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}sagashite ita kyou to chigatte{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.12,0:23:19.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm sure you'd laugh at my disappointment{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.12,0:23:19.25,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}ochikonnde shimau boku wo warau no darou{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.14,0:23:37.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Having defeated Hyunckel, Dai and company{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.31,0:23:41.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}along with Baduck, meet Amy,\None of the Papnica Troika.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.15,0:23:45.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Together, they head to Valge Island\Nwhere Leona awaits.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.77,0:23:51.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But the island is already under siege by\Ntheir next enemy, the Blizzblaze Legion.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.36,0:23:54.99,Default,,0,0,0,,DRAGON QUEST The Adventure of Dai{\i1},{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.16,0:23:57.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"Blizzblaze General Flazzard"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.79,0:23:59.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The adventure continues!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.66,0:24:01.67,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.67,0:24:03.66,Default,,0,0,0,,
